    <title>Circus/FleaCircus.pm</title>

    <para>Circus::FleaCircus is a class representing a fleacircus.
    (you guessed that, right?)</para>

    <para>Beeing derived from Foo::Circus, it is composed of flea,
    trainer, audience und showroom instances, and implements
    methods to steer these.</para>

