        <para>Circus::FleaCircus-&gt;new($numOfFleas,
        $context)</para>
      </section>

      <section>
        <title>PARAMETER</title>

        <para>$numOfFleas: the number of fleaobjects
        instantiated</para>

        <para>$context: reference to context hash</para>
      </section>

      <section>
        <title>RETURNS</title>

        <para>$fleaCircus: FleaCircus object</para>
      </section>

      <section>
        <title>DESCRIPTION</title>

        <para>Constructor</para>

        <para>The SuperClass Foo::Circus still takes care of most
